    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 981-generation Porsche Cayman S represents the pinnacle of mid-engine balance. Powered by a 3.4L naturally aspirated DFI flat-six, the drivetrain delivers 325 hp through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle and a mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), offering variable damping rates for optimized cornering kinematics. Braking is handled by four-piston monobloc aluminum calipers over cross-drilled rotors, ensuring minimal thermal fade. Maintained with technical rigor, the vehicle exhibits excellent compression and a clean rev history. Minor cosmetic patina present, but the mechanical vitals\u2014including the cooling system and bushings\u2014are in robust condition.",
      "price": 36500.0,
