      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2011 BMW M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. This example excels in performance metrics, with the individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous response up to the 8,400 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized: rod bearings have been replaced and throttle actuators serviced to ensure long-term powertrain reliability. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain and subframe integrity remain excellent. A transparently maintained platform for the purist seeking the final chapter of atmospheric M-power.",
